    public class HeaterTemperaturesSensorData
extends fr.sorbonne_u.alasca.physical_data.ComposedSignalData
implements HeaterSensorDataI
    The class HeaterTemperaturesSensor implements a composed sensor data sent by the heater to the controller, which contains the target temperature and the current room temperature measured by the heater internal thermometer.
